nt genre-designation’, 2002), also included in the present volume.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aApostelgeschichte. 4aEuthalianischer Apparat. 4aHermann von Soden. 4aKatholische Briefe. 4aPaulus. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh  aActs.  aCatholic Letters.  aEuthalian Apparatus.  aHermann von Soden.  aPaul.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Theology and Religious Studies 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023854908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE THEOLOGY, JUDAISM, RELIGION  2012z978311029384508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET THEOLOGIE,RELIGIONSWISS., JUDAISTIK  2012z9783110288957oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311029179740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311029196440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110291964423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110291964/original  a978-3-11-023854-9  DGBA Backlist Theology and Religious Studies 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-029384-5  E-BOOK PACKAGE THEOLOGY, JUDAISM, RELIGION  2012b2012  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2012  aZDB-23-DGGb2012  aZDB-23-GTRc2000d2014